HIGHLIGHTS
==========

Web interface that query R2R to extract saliency from documents

to build it:

$ clone <repo>
$ cd highlights
$ docker-compose build


you can access the tool at:

http://localhost:8282/index.html


==========================

ATTENTION: code deployment isn't complete it may not to work


ARCHITECTURE:
--------------

nginx inverse-proxy serve a react.js frontend

react.js frontend query R2R microservice and FRED remote api to parse document
docker-compose orchestrate the comunication




